<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">

<title>Flames Website</title>

<style>
    * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
    }

    body {
        margin: 0;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, #86f1ff, #ffd3f8);
        padding: 12px;
    }

    .card {
        background: white;
        padding: 24px 20px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        width: 100%;
        max-width: 380px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    h2 {
        margin-top: 0;
        font-size: clamp(20px, 5vw, 26px);
        color: #333;
    }

    label {
        display: block;
        margin-top: 10px;
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #444;
    }

    input[type="text"] {
        width: 100%;
        padding: 12px;
        margin-top: 5px;
        border-radius: 10px;
        border: 1px solid #bfbfbf;
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    /* Custom gender buttons */
    .gender-toggle {
        display: flex;
        gap: 12px;
        margin-top: 8px;
        justify-content: center;
        flex-wrap: wrap;
    }

    .gender-toggle input[type="radio"] {
        display: none;
    }

    .gender-toggle label {
        padding: 10px 20px;
        border-radius: 30px;
        border: 1px solid #00bcd4;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #00bcd4;
        transition: all 0.2s ease;
        user-select: none;
        min-width: 80px;
        text-align: center;
    }

    .gender-toggle input[type="radio"]:checked + label {
        background-color: #00bcd4;
        color: white;
        box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
    }

    button {
        margin-top: 18px;
        width: 100%;
        padding: 12px;
        border: none;
        border-radius: 12px;
        cursor: pointer;
        font-weight: bold;
        background-color: #00bcd4;
        color: white;
        font-size: 15px;
        transition: transform 0.1s ease;
    }

    button:active {
        transform: scale(0.97);
    }

    .funny-text {
        margin-top: 12px;
        font-size: 12px;
        color: #555;
    }

    @media (max-width: 360px){
        .card {
            padding: 16px 12px;
        }

        input[type="text"], button {
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .gender-toggle label {
            font-size: 13px;
            padding: 8px 16px;
            min-width: 70px;
        }
    }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">
    <h2>üî• FLAMES Checker</h2>

    <form action="/user" method="POST">
        <!-- Your Name -->
        <label>Your Name</label>
        <input type="text" name="name" required minlength="4" placeholder="Enter your name">

        <!-- Your Gender -->
        <label>Your Gender:</label>
        <div class="gender-toggle">
            <input type="radio" id="male1" name="gender1" value="Male" required>
            <label for="male1">Male</label>

            <input type="radio" id="female1" name="gender1" value="Female">
            <label for="female1">Female</label>
        </div>

        <!-- Friend's Name -->
        <label>Your Friend's Name</label>
        <input type="text" name="FrdName" required minlength="4" placeholder="Enter friend's name">

        <!-- Friend's Gender -->
        <label>Friend's Gender:</label>
        <div class="gender-toggle">
            <input type="radio" id="male2" name="gender2" value="Male" required>
            <label for="male2">Male</label>

            <input type="radio" id="female2" name="gender2" value="Female">
            <label for="female2">Female</label>
        </div>

        <button type="submit">Check Result</button>
    </form>

    <div class="funny-text">
        üòÑ Don‚Äôt worry‚Ä¶ even if FLAMES says ‚ÄúEnemies‚Äù, you still have to attend the same class together!
    </div>
</div>

</body>
</html>
